    <item>
      <title>Redwood 计划为“对抗性”信贷市场设立 22.5 亿美元基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/redwood-plans-2-25-billion-fund-for-adversarial-credit-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博社看到的一封致投资者的信显示，Redwood Capital Management 是一家规模 94 亿美元的对冲基金，专注于信贷和特殊情况的机会性投资，该基金正在寻求为其下一支提取基金再筹集 22.5 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/redwood-plans-2-25-billion-fund-for-adversarial-credit-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 18:35:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰晤士水务公司推迟竞购 33 亿英镑股权的最后期限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/thames-water-pushes-deadline-in-hunt-for-3-3-billion-in-equity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰晤士水务公司延长了寻求数十亿英镑新股权的最后期限，因为它要求潜在投资者提供更多帮助这家陷入困境的公用事业公司摆脱困境的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/thames-water-pushes-deadline-in-hunt-for-3-3-billion-in-equity</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 18:30:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约交通局批准征收 9 美元拥堵费</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/new-york-s-transit-agency-approves-9-congestion-pricing-toll</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大都会运输署批准了曼哈顿的交通拥堵收费修改计划，但当选总统唐纳德·特朗普威胁称，一旦上任，他将终止该计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/new-york-s-transit-agency-approves-9-congestion-pricing-toll</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 18:17:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
