      <title>高盛认为，在新的关税制度下，美元将“长期走强”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/goldman-sees-dollar-stronger-for-longer-in-a-new-tariff-regime</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团的货币策略师表示，受唐纳德·特朗普计划征收高额关税的推动，美元正进入新的走强时期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/goldman-sees-dollar-stronger-for-longer-in-a-new-tariff-regime</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 18:04:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛重申 2025 年金价 3,000 美元目标，金价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/gold-rebounds-after-deep-weekly-loss-with-rate-outlook-in-flux</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团重申明年金价将达到每盎司 3,000 美元的预测，黄金价格创下 8 月份以来的最大涨幅，分析师建议投资者“购买黄金”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/gold-rebounds-after-deep-weekly-loss-with-rate-outlook-in-flux</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 01:19:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特斯拉推动股市上涨，电动汽车巨头股价飙升 5%：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/asian-stocks-eye-soft-start-as-fed-doubts-simmer-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国国债收益率在 10 年期国债收益率接近 4.5% 后趋于稳定，股市在上周下跌之后出现反弹，交易员密切关注当选总统唐纳德·特朗普政府的新闻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/asian-stocks-eye-soft-start-as-fed-doubts-simmer-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Nov 2024 22:32:23 GMT</pubDate>
